  "texts": [
    "In case examples for an infrequent label ℓ P Y are not found in Xi.d.",
    ", we exclude it from the computation of pi.d..",
    "The goal of this normalization is to enhance the metric's interpretability across tasks of varying difficulty.",
    "Specifically, nonsensical task inputs made up of random words as in DC, or placeholder-like strings as in CC, are less likely to be observed during instruction tuning.",
    "We leave all other demonstrations in their original order."
